    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black Metallic. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory M-Variable differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically, the vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension remains tight with original bushings and Bilstein dampers, while the cross-drilled rotors and multi-piston calipers offer fade-free deceleration. This is a collector-grade specimen with zero deferred maintenance and flawless factory paint depth.",
