      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that remains in absolute showroom condition. This car has been meticulously maintained by a single owner and has been strictly garage-kept under a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with zero imperfections, scratches, or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium upholstery is free of any creases, the carpets are spotless, and the interior still carries that distinctive factory-fresh scent. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule with all service performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. Every button, feature, and electronic system operates exactly as intended. Complete with all original keys, manuals, and a comprehensive service history folder, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for a buyer seeking a flawless, collector-grade example.",
